{"tid":2203260,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"葉劉嘆富豪賣樓求去對港失信心遭田少寸爆：講到好似同自己無關咁！","createTime":"2020-09-15T08:18:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T11:29:12.000Z","uid":240362,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1060a61a908ce45d621dd1aaa9750a6f75ff682c","tid":2203260,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T08:18:31.000Z","msg":"有時，架可能真係自己丟㗎。身兼行政會議成員嘅新民黨主席葉劉淑儀噚日（14日）喺Facebook發帖，話喺港島寶雲道行山時，沿途見到唔少燈柱、欄杆同埋涼亭，都貼滿豪宅盤廣告，部份講明係「割價」、「急售」，佢即時專家上身，話反映香港已出現令人憂心嘅社會現象、有人對香港缺乏信心甚至徹底死心、對香港明顯響起「信心危機」警號，話特區政府要想方法並有實際行動，令香港市民同自世界各地嘅人士，對香港重拾信心及希望。<br />\n<br />\n同樣做過行會成員、持續積極高度關注葉劉一舉一動嘅自由黨榮譽主席田北俊睇唔過眼，即時分享葉劉帖文，反問乜佢冇責任咩：「（葉劉）仲問點解香港搞成咁嘅？啲行政會議議員講到好似同自己冇關係咁樣。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200915/UOBJQTYQQZHKTBSW4E77CLRM7M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200915%2FUOBJQTYQQZHKTBSW4E77CLRM7M%2F&d=ulKCtXgG4rwmRR8qyGKIuYVlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=5ff1ca3f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200915%2FUOBJQTYQQZHKTBSW4E77CLRM7M%2F&h=dc80ccd8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200915/UOBJQTYQQZHKTBSW4E77CLRM7M/</a>"},{"pid":"9f043a40419745bd707c935a344f5376d7e7eff8","tid":2203260,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T08:22:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebde0885fb661c9a02f7cedde43c185cbacf4f1b","tid":2203260,"uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T08:22:56.000Z","msg":"啲行政會議議員講到好似同自己冇關係咁樣。"},{"pid":"137b3a62bc31c55676c20e80a6788d77f97ea4e0","tid":2203260,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f043a40419745bd707c935a344f5376d7e7eff8